# Build-context excludes for the CRM2 images. Keep source (apps/packages/db) +
# manifests; drop installed deps (re-installed fresh in-image), build output,
# caches, secrets, and docs.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.vite
.git
.github
*.md
**/*.md
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!**/.env.example
**/secrets
*.log
.DS_Store
